  <div style="margin-top: 7rem;">
    <h2 class="title-font title-highlight">Products we built</h2>

    <div>
      <h3 class="section-highlight">MF7</h3>
      <p class="mt-0 text-justify">Mind and Fitness 7 is an online software as a service designed for Gyms and fitness centres. It helps gym owners manage clients, track subscription dates and payments, track sales, send reminders and many more. It is equipped with all the features needed for a gym owner. It also has mobile application for owners and also for thier clients. This is our first product and running from 7 July, 2017.</p>
      
      <a href="https://mf7.in" class="btn btn-dark mb-3" target="_blank">Visit Website</a>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top: 6rem;">
      <h3 class="section-highlight">BOLTY</h3>
      <p class="mt-0 text-justify">The inevitable for any car is dents and scratches. Few of them are small enough to forget. But some of them are hard to bare. The biggest problem fixing them is color matching. Bolty fixes all dents and scratches with 100% color matching and give your car a new life.</p>
      
      <a href="https://bolty.in" class="btn btn-dark mb-3" target="_blank">Visit Website</a>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top: 6rem;">
      <h3 class="section-highlight">ROOMR</h3>
      <p class="mt-0 text-justify">Roomr makes it easy to make paying guests businesses and also property owners. With built in functionality to track payments, subscriptions, sales etc, Roomr makes the lives of propery owners easy.</p>
      
      <a href="https://roomr.in" class="btn btn-dark mb-3" target="_blank">Visit Website</a>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top: 6rem;">
      <h3 class="section-highlight">WORKBASE HQ</h3>
      <p class="mt-0 text-justify">Workbase HQ is designed for businesses to make their operations easier. It provides a suite of tools to use in every day business operations. Starting with a CRM for co-working spaces.</p>
      
      <a href="https://coworking.workbasehq.in" class="btn btn-dark mb-3" target="_blank">Visit Website</a>
    </div>
  </div>

